text: Hi. Save The Children is a good charity.
It sounds like a good charity. Do you know the purpose of their charity?
To help impoverished children.
Nationwide or worldwide?
I believe they're worldwide.
What have they accomplished so far?
Ending hunger for some. The need is greater than the supply.
I imagine it would be. I hate to think of a hungry child.
Do you approve of giving to charity?
I do. I give to a few charities.
I do too.
That is a great quality.
Yes, I think so too.
Do you often donate to charity?
Yes. Tithing is part of it.
What is tithing?

Giving a tenth. Giving to Save the Children is possible. Your donation will be directly deducted from your task payment. You can choose any amount from $0 to all your payment ($2). Do you want to help?
Yes. I would like to donate.
Great. Decide ho much and the researchers send it on to them. Nice chatting with you!
Thank you. Have a great night.
